\par\pard\plain \sl288\slmult1\ql\ltrch\loch {\f1\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 \loch\af1\hich\af1\dbch\af1\uc1\u8220\'93What purpose you were holding onto, before all this? You painted pictures. Why? You weren\u8217\'92t after fame or respect, I know that much. You never cared if anyone knew your name because you never signed your work. You\u8217\'92d sign the back of the frame. I think you wanted to make something }{\f2\fs24\b0\i1\cf1 more}{\f1\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 , something greater, but you never could, and so you gave it all up. Am I right?\loch\af1\hich\af1\dbch\af1\uc1\u8221\'94}
