\par\pard\plain \sl288\slmult1\ltrch\loch {\f1\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 \loch\af1\hich\af1\dbch\af1\uc1\u8220\'93I didn\u8217\'92t think you were going to do it. ,\u8221\'94 Vigram said. His was stern, but his eyes were smiling. }
\par\plain {\f1\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 \loch\af1\hich\af1\dbch\af1\uc1\u8220\'93I made my decision,\u8221\'94 Mandri said.}
