\par\plain {\f1\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 \loch\af1\hich\af1\dbch\af1\uc1\u8220\'93Ow!\u8221\'94 Mandri moaned as Vigram kicked his shin again. \u8220\'93Vigram, you don\u8217\'92t know me well enough to intervene here!\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f1\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 Without asking if Mandri minded, Vigram unshouldered a folded stool and sat it down on it. This disturbed Gil, who raised his heavy head. The ox saw the Vigram, then Lora, then gave a snort, then promptly went back to sleep. }}